Delicious, but with some minor changes. Used 1 pound Russets, cubed, parboiled 6 minutes, then well-browned in cast-iron skillet with the fat. Used 2 TBS capers. Used 2 TBS sour cream. (Was afraid to drown out the smoked salmon taste). Topped w/ chopped parsley. Well received by the family. Thanks!

